# US-001: Amazon Product Search

## Story Details
- **ID**: SCRUM-201
- **Priority**: Medium
- **Sprint**: TBD
- **Status**: Ready for Testing

## User Story Statement
**As a** customer  
**I want to** search for a water bottle on Amazon  
**So that** I can view available product options

## Story Description
Implement a simple product search flow that allows users to navigate to Amazon's homepage, enter a product keyword ("water bottle"), and view relevant search results. The feature must be reliable, performant, and display accurate product information.

## Application Under Test
| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Base URL** | https://www.amazon.com |
| **Feature Path** | / (Homepage) |
| **Login Required** | No |
| **Test User** | N/A |

---

## Acceptance Criteria

### AC1: Homepage Navigation
**Given** I am a user visiting Amazon  
**When** I open the Amazon homepage  
**Then** I should see the search bar displayed prominently at the top of the page

### AC2: Search Execution
**Given** I am on the Amazon homepage  
**When** I enter "water bottle" in the search bar  
**And** click the search button  
**Then** I should be redirected to the search results page with correct query parameter  
**And** the page URL should contain the search keyword

### AC3: Results Display
**Given** I have searched for "water bottle"  
**When** the results page loads successfully  
**Then** I should see a list of products related to water bottles  
**And** each product should display its name, price, image, and customer rating

### AC4: Error Handling
**Given** I am on the Amazon homepage  
**When** I enter an invalid or empty search term  
**Then** I should see an appropriate error message or "no results found" notification  
**And** the page should not crash or redirect unexpectedly  
**And** I should be able to perform a new search

---

## Business Rules
- Search bar must be accessible and visible on the homepage
- Search results must display only products relevant to the keyword
- No login/authentication required for basic product search
- Page must load within 5 seconds under normal network conditions
- Search should support special characters and multi-word queries
- Results should be sorted by relevance (default sorting)
- Maximum 20 results displayed per page

---

## Technical Notes
- **Automation Tool**: Playwright
- **Target Browsers**: Chrome, Firefox, Safari
- **Key Validations**:
  - Search bar visibility and clickability
  - Search results page load without errors
  - Product listing accuracy (name, price, image, rating present)
  - No JavaScript console errors
  - Network requests complete successfully
- **Performance SLA**: Page load ≤ 5 seconds (under standard network)
- **Test Execution**: Cross-browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari)

---

## Test Scenarios

| # | Scenario | Expected Result |
